	I wind up and give the thing a dramatic smash.  I was expecting it to crack or something, but the whole thing shattered into about a billion pieces.\
	\'93That was about the fucking STUPIDEST thing you could have done!\'94 Lauren shouts at me, angrily brushing little shards of class off of her, putting her shirt back on.  She just stormed out and the laughter kept going except it sounded like it was coming from everywhere.  I swept for days, weeks, but I know I didn\'92t get all of it because sometime when I\'92m in there I still hear giggles.  Girls won\'92t even come near the place.  I can\'92t even sleep.  I swear they can still see me.}